  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "ch37-01",
      "text": "Pops a commis une erreur.",
      "imagePrompt": "On a steampunk rooftop, old Pops sits beside Avril facing the viewer, his head bowed in confession, the smoky Paris skyline stretching behind them. Pops's weathered, regretful face is the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Moonlight and distant city gaslights illuminate the scene, remorseful and quiet mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "mistake",
      "speaker": "Pops"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch37-02",
      "text": "C'est une belle erreur.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "mistake",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch37-03",
      "text": "L'erreur que Pops a commise est belle.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "mistake",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch37-04",
      "text": "Pops regarde Avril parce qu'il a peur.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "mistake",
      "speaker": "Pops"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch37-05",
      "text": "C'est la vie, mais la mort arrive.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "mistake",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch37-06",
      "text": "La vieillesse est là.",
      "imagePrompt": "On the rooftop, Pops holds up his wrinkled hands facing the viewer, Avril sitting young and bright beside him, steampunk chimneys rising behind them. Pops's aged, wrinkled hands contrasting with Avril's youth are the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Soft moonlight washes over both figures, reflective and bittersweet mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "old_age",
      "speaker": "Pops"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch37-07",
      "text": "La mort est au-dessus.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "old_age",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch37-08",
      "text": "La vieillesse arrive comme la nuit.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "old_age",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch37-09",
      "text": "Au-dessus, la nuit rappelle la mort.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "old_age",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch37-10",
      "text": "Pops pense à la mort.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "old_age",
      "speaker": "Pops"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch37-11",
      "text": "C'est beau ici.",
      "imagePrompt": "On the rooftop, Avril and Pops sit side by side facing the viewer, smiling gently as a rare break in the smog reveals stars above the steampunk skyline. The patch of clear starry sky above them is the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Moonlight and starlight cast a silvery glow, peaceful and beautiful mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "beauty",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch37-12",
      "text": "La forme est belle.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "beauty",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch37-13",
      "text": "La forme est belle car la vie continue.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "beauty",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch37-14",
      "text": "On voit la forme de la vie.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "beauty",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch37-15",
      "text": "Le monde est beau.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "beauty",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch37-16",
      "text": "Ça va péter !",
